text: dutaru, visvasigalannu mattu satkarmigalannu kattaleyinda horatandu belakinedege munnadesalikkagi, nimage allahana suspasta vacanagalannu odi kelisuttare. Allahanalli visvasavittu satkarma madidavanannu avanu taladalli nadigalu hariyuttiruva svargodyanadolage serisuvanu. Avaru sadakala alle iruvaru. Allahanu avarige dharala sampannateyannu niduvanu
